author: Michael Nedelman, CNN
title: Study: Covid-19 cases in Santa Clara, California, may be 85 times higher than reported
description: Far more people may have been infected with Covid-19 than have been confirmed by health officials in Santa Clara County, California, according to a study released Friday in preprint.
content:
